  "5": {
    "chapterId": 5,
    "title": "介系詞",
    "page": 58,
    "subLessons": [
      {
        "id": "5-1",
        "title": "時間介系詞",
        "teaching": {
          "explanation": "<b>at/on/in 依時間長短分工</b><br>at、on、in 是三個最基本的時間介系詞，依「時間長短」分工：at 用在最短的時間點，on 用在天/日期，in 用在較長的時間（月、季、年）。<br><br><b>完整規則表</b><br>【at】較短的時間點：at 8:30、at noon、at night（＝in the night）、at midnight、at Christmas<br>【on】日子：on Monday、on July 9、on my birthday、on Christmas Day、on the weekend、on Tuesday afternoon（＝on the afternoon of Tuesday）<br>【in】較長的時間：in a week、in July、in spring/summer/fall/winter、in 2012、in the morning/afternoon/evening<br>【in+數字+時間單位】「在…之後」：in ten minutes、in three seconds<br>【during】「在…期間」，強調過程：during this week、during the movie<br>【by】「最遲在…之前」，有期限性：by tomorrow、by next year<br>【through】「自始至終」，從頭到尾：through the whole year<br>【from...to...】「從…到…」：from eight to eleven o'clock<br>【after/past ＝ 分鐘＜30】at a quarter after/past three（三點十五分）<br>【to/of ＝ 分鐘＞30】at a quarter to/of nine（八點四十五分）<br>【between】兩個時間之間：between one and two o'clock<br>【about/around】大約：about five o'clock<br><br><b>這些地方最容易出錯</b><br>① every、last、next、this/that/these/those 前面的時間副詞不加 at/on/in：last week、next year（不加介系詞）。<br>② 主詞若是「時間」本身則不加介系詞；主詞若是「事件/活動」則要加介系詞：It is 8:30.（無介系詞）vs. The game is at 8:30.（加at）。<br>③ 日期完整順序：on＋星期, 月日, 年（on Saturday, December 20th, 2011）。<br>④ 屬於大時間裡的小時間：the+小時間+of+大時間（in the spring of 2009）。<br>⑤ tomorrow 前不加 in/on/at，若要表達「之前」用 by（by tomorrow）。<br>⑥ during 強調某事發生的「期間」，through 強調「從頭到尾都持續」。<br>⑦ around 和 about 意思相同，都表示「大約」。<br>⑧ 特殊節日或假日一律搭配 on（on Thanksgiving、on Chinese New Year）。<br><br><b>額外要注意的細節</b><br>① in time「來得及」vs on time「準時」意思不同：We arrived just in time for the show.（勉強來得及）vs The train left on time.（準時）<br>② at the same time「同時」是固定片語，強調兩件事同一時刻發生。",
          "examples": [
            {
              "en": "The movie starts at 7:30 tonight.",
              "zh": "電影今晚七點半開始。"
            },
            {
              "en": "We are meeting on Saturday morning.",
              "zh": "我們星期六早上要碰面。"
            },
            {
              "en": "School begins in September.",
              "zh": "開學是九月。"
            },
            {
              "en": "I'll finish this in twenty minutes.",
              "zh": "我再二十分鐘就會完成這件事。"
            },
            {
              "en": "She stayed up during the whole storm.",
              "zh": "她整個暴風雨期間都沒睡。"
            },
            {
              "en": "Please submit the form by Friday.",
              "zh": "請最晚在星期五前繳交表格。"
            },
            {
              "en": "He worked through the entire night to finish the project.",
              "zh": "他整晚沒睡把這個專案做完。"
            },
            {
              "en": "We chatted for hours between classes.",
              "zh": "我們下課時間聊了好幾個小時。"
            },
            {
              "en": "We got to the airport just in time to catch our flight.",
              "zh": "我們及時趕到機場搭上了班機。"
            },
            {
              "en": "The two singers started singing at the same time.",
              "zh": "這兩位歌手同時開始唱歌。"
            }
          ]
        },
