            },
            {
              "en": "I often think of my childhood friends.",
              "zh": "我常常想起我小時候的朋友。"
            },
            {
              "en": "He's thinking about changing his job.",
              "zh": "他正在考慮換工作。"
            },
            {
              "en": "Don't worry about the test; you'll do fine.",
              "zh": "別擔心考試，你會考好的。"
            },
            {
              "en": "Whether we go hiking depends on the weather tomorrow.",
              "zh": "我們是否去健行取決於明天的天氣。"
            },
            {
              "en": "She knows how to deal with difficult customers calmly.",
              "zh": "她知道如何冷靜地處理難搞的顧客。"
            }
          ]
