            },
            {
              "en": "The baby is finally asleep after crying for an hour.",
              "zh": "寶寶哭了一個小時後終於睡著了。"
            },
            {
              "en": "That was such a difficult decision to make.",
              "zh": "那真是一個很難做的決定。"
            },
            {
              "en": "She looked nervous before her speech.",
              "zh": "她在演講前看起來很緊張。"
            },
            {
              "en": "The news made my grandmother very happy.",
              "zh": "這則消息讓我奶奶非常開心。"
