      {
        "id": "7-10",
        "title": "常用的「形容詞＋介系詞」的連用片語",
        "teaching": {
          "explanation": "<b>常見「形容詞+介系詞」固定搭配</b><br>be afraid of害怕、be good at擅長、be famous for因…著名、be different from不同於、be full of充滿、be proud of以…為榮、be worried about擔心、be tired of厭倦、be busy with忙於、be crazy about對…著迷、be popular with/among受…歡迎、be ready for準備好、be short of缺少、be similar to跟…類似、be made of/from由…製成。<br><br><b>字義相近的形容詞怎麼分</b><br>① tall（有生命體/可測量高度）vs high（無生命體/不可測得的高度）：Tom is 1.7 meters tall. / Stars are high in the sky.<br>② large（面積範圍大）vs big（體積重量大，較口語）：a large Coke / a big man<br>③ small（體型小）vs little（無形事物的小，或帶情感色彩）：a small dog / my little sister<br>④ few/a few修飾可數名詞複數；little/a little修飾不可數名詞：few friends / a little money<br><br><b>be made of / from / by / with的差別</b><br>be made of：材質沒有經過化學變化，看得出原本的樣子：The chair is made of wood.<br>be made from：材質經過化學變化，看不出原本的樣子：Wine is made from grapes.<br>be made by+人：強調製作者是誰。<br>be made with+工具/材料：強調使用的工具或原料。<br><br><b>易混淆重點</b><br>① price（價錢）只有high/low之分，沒有expensive/cheap的用法搭配price這個字本身（price is high，不會說price is expensive，要說the price is expensive這種說法其實也可以，但书中強調price常態用high/low）。<br>② be angry about+事、be angry at/with+人，兩者搭配的介系詞不同，別搞混。",
          "examples": [
            {
              "en": "This restaurant is famous for its delicious desserts.",
