              "en": "My little sister is crazy about dinosaurs these days.",
              "zh": "我妹妹最近對恐龍很著迷。"
            },
            {
              "en": "The singer is popular among teenagers around the world.",
              "zh": "這位歌手在全世界的青少年之間很受歡迎。"
