      {
        "id": "8-2",
        "title": "情狀副詞",
        "teaching": {
          "explanation": "<b>情狀副詞怎麼改</b><br>由形容詞字尾加ly變成：一般直接加ly（quick→quickly）；字尾y去y加ily（happy→happily）；字尾le去e加y（terrible→terribly）；字尾ue去e加ly（true→truly）；字尾ll直接加y（full→fully）。有些形容詞和副詞同形：early、late、fast、hard、high、far、near。<br><br><b>特殊變化最容易搞混</b><br>① good的副詞是well（不是goodly），friendly則是形容詞（不是副詞）。<br>② 同形字加ly後意思完全改變：late（遲的）→lately（最近）；hard（努力的）→hardly（幾乎不）；near（近的）→nearly（幾乎，=almost）；short（矮的）→shortly（很快、不久）；high（高的）→highly（崇高地）。<br>③ 名詞加ly不是副詞而是形容詞：day→daily（每天的）、friend→friendly（友善的）、love→lovely（可愛的）。<br><br><b>情狀副詞放在句子的哪裡</b><br>① 一般放句尾：Tom usually goes to school early.<br>② 只能放在不及物動詞後：She walks carefully in the park.（不能說She carefully walks）<br>③ 進行式/被動式中可放V-ing或p.p.前後：They are happily playing basketball. = They are playing basketball happily.<br>④ 不可插在及物動詞跟受詞中間：只能說He opened the window quietly.或He quietly opened the window，不能說He opened quietly the window。<br>⑤ 可拆式動詞片語（turn on、take off）中間不可插入情狀副詞：只能Mandy turned on the music slowly.或Mandy slowly turned on the music，不能turned on slowly the music。但不可拆式片語（listen to、look at）中間可以插入：Susan listened to the music happily. = Susan listened happily to the music.<br>⑥ 修飾形容詞或副詞時放在被修飾的字前面：He is dangerously ill.<br>⑦ 修飾整句話時放在句子最前面：Luckily, he came back safely.<br><br><b>與形容詞同形的副詞只能放動詞後</b><br>hard、early、late、fast、high、far這些字當副詞用時，只能放在動詞後面：He works hard.（不能說He hardly works表示「他很努力工作」，hardly意思完全不同）",
