      {
        "id": "9-2",
        "title": "形容詞的最高級",
        "teaching": {
          "explanation": "<b>什麼時候用最高級</b><br>三者以上做比較時使用，最高級前面一定要加the。<br><br><b>規則變化</b><br>單音節字尾加est：small→the smallest；字尾e加st：large→the largest；短母音+子音重複字尾：big→the biggest；子音+y去y加iest：pretty→the prettiest；兩音節以上前面加(the) most/least：beautiful→the most beautiful。<br><br><b>不規則變化</b><br>good/well→best；many/much→most；bad/ill→worst；little→least（注意：few→fewest）。<br><br><b>基本句構</b><br>A+be+the+最高級+of the three/在一群人事物中：Mary is the youngest of the three.<br><br><b>最高級可以怎麼加強語氣</b><br>much、by far、the very（只修飾-est結尾的最高級）：Jeff is by far the smartest boy.<br><br><b>最高級不用「其他」的概念</b><br>因為最高級本來就是跟全部人事物比，不需要再排除自己：Taipei is the biggest city in Taiwan.（不用說the biggest of all the other cities）<br><br><b>比較級跟最高級可以互相改寫</b><br>Tokyo is the biggest city in the world. = Tokyo is bigger than any other city in the world. = Tokyo is bigger than all the other cities in the world. = No other city in the world is as big as Tokyo. = No other city in the world is bigger than Tokyo.<br><br><b>常考片語</b><br>do/try one's best「盡力而為」；at best「充其量」；at least「至少」；at last「終於」；best of all「最好的是」；worst of all「最糟的是」。",
