        "title": "情狀副詞的級",
        "teaching": {
          "explanation": "<b>情狀副詞也有比較級跟最高級</b><br>跟形容詞不同的是，情狀副詞比較級只能在前面加more（不能字尾加ier），最高級只能在前面加(the) most（不能字尾加iest）：quickly→more quickly→(the) most quickly。<br><br><b>跟形容詞同形的副詞例外</b><br>fast、hard、late、early、high、far這些字當副詞用時，比較級最高級跟形容詞一樣直接變化：faster/the fastest、harder/the hardest、earlier/the earliest、higher/the highest、farther/the farthest（距離）、further/the furthest（程度）。<br><br><b>good/well 和 bad/badly共用同一組變化</b><br>形容詞good、副詞well都共用better/best；形容詞bad、副詞badly都共用worse/worst。<br><br><b>放的位置</b><br>情狀副詞的比較級、最高級都只能放在動詞後面：I walk much faster than anyone else in my family. / David studies (the) hardest.（副詞最高級前面的the有時可以省略，跟形容詞最高級不同）<br><br><b>原級比較怎麼用</b><br>跟形容詞的句構一樣，用as+副詞原級+as，一樣放在動詞後面：I like fishing as much as my father (does). / Jeremy did as well as the others on the test.<br><br><b>常用慣用語</b><br>as...as possible / as...as one can「盡可能地…」：I'll do it as soon as possible.；數字+times+as...as「是…的幾倍」：Mandy's house is three times as big as mine.",
          "examples": [
            {
              "en": "She speaks English more fluently than I do.",
              "zh": "她說英文比我流利。"
            },
            {
              "en": "Of all the runners, he finished the race most quickly.",
              "zh": "在所有跑者中，他最快完成比賽。"
            },
            {
              "en": "My brother arrived earlier than everyone else.",
              "zh": "我弟弟比其他所有人都早到。"
            },
            {
              "en": "Please explain this more clearly, if you can.",
              "zh": "如果可以的話，請把這個解釋得更清楚一點。"
            },
            {
              "en": "Of the three singers, she sang the most beautifully.",
              "zh": "在這三位歌手中，她唱得最美。"
            },
            {
              "en": "He did well on the test, but she did even better.",
              "zh": "他考得不錯，但她考得更好。"
            },
            {
              "en": "Please reply as soon as possible.",
              "zh": "請盡快回覆。"
            },
            {
              "en": "This car runs twice as fast as that old one.",
              "zh": "這輛車跑得比那輛舊車快兩倍。"
            },
            {
              "en": "I try to exercise as often as I can.",
              "zh": "我盡量常常運動。"
            },
            {
              "en": "He worked the hardest among all the workers.",
              "zh": "在所有工人中，他工作最努力。"
            }
          ]
        },
