              "en": "I felt embarrassed when I forgot his name.",
              "zh": "我忘記他的名字時感到很尷尬。"
            },
            {
              "en": "This puzzle is becoming more confusing to me.",
              "zh": "這個謎題對我來說變得越來越令人困惑。"
            },
            {
              "en": "She was satisfied with her test results.",
              "zh": "她對自己的考試成績感到滿意。"
            },
