            },
            {
              "en": "The old fence needs painting before winter comes.",
              "zh": "冬天來臨前，這道舊籬笆需要被上漆。"
            },
            {
              "en": "The problem kept being ignored by the committee.",
              "zh": "這個問題一直被委員會忽略。"
            },
            {
              "en": "This song deserves to be remembered for years.",
              "zh": "這首歌值得被記住很多年。"
            },
            {
              "en": "The road still needs to be fixed after the flood.",
              "zh": "洪水過後，這條路還需要被修復。"
            },
