              "en": "She heard someone knock on the door twice.",
              "zh": "她聽到有人敲了兩次門。"
            },
            {
              "en": "I felt my phone buzzing in my pocket.",
              "zh": "我感覺到我的手機在口袋裡震動。"
            },
            {
              "en": "Did you notice him leave early today?",
              "zh": "你有注意到他今天早退嗎？"
            },
            {
              "en": "I smelled something burning in the kitchen.",
              "zh": "我聞到廚房裡有東西燒焦的味道。"
            },
