              "en": "Sorry, you have to pay in cash.",
              "zh": "抱歉，你必須付現金。"
            },
            {
              "en": "Yesterday Mom bought me an MP3 player.",
              "zh": "昨天媽媽買了一台 MP3 給我。"
            },
            {
              "en": "I bought the book for only 20 dollars.",
              "zh": "我只花 20 元買這本書。"
            },
            {
              "en": "It took our whole class an entire week to finish the project.",
              "zh": "我們全班花了整整一週才完成這項專案。"
