            },
            {
              "en": "What do you usually do after school on Fridays?",
              "zh": "你星期五放學後通常都做什麼？"
            },
            {
              "en": "Which tastes better, the mango cake or the cheese cake?",
              "zh": "哪一個比較好吃，芒果蛋糕還是起司蛋糕？"
            },
            {
              "en": "Who do you think will win the singing contest this year?",
