            "title": "Planning the Class Trip",
            "passage": "Our class is planning a one-day trip, and everyone has a lot of questions. \"__(1)__ place should we go to, the zoo or the museum?\" asked Amy. The teacher smiled and said, \"__(2)__ activity do you all enjoy most?\" Some students wanted to see animals, others wanted art. \"__(3)__ month is best for the trip, May or June?\" Ben wondered, because the weather matters. Then Cindy pointed at a lost cap on the floor and asked, \"__(4)__ cap is this? Someone should take it.\" Finally, the teacher asked, \"__(5)__ time should we meet at the school gate?\" We all agreed on eight o'clock. \"And __(6)__ bus do we take, the blue one or the red one?\" Ken added with a grin.",
