      {
        "id": "16-4",
        "title": "由 how 延伸出的疑問副詞片語",
        "teaching": {
          "explanation": "<b>為什麼 how 變化最多</b><br>how 本身問「如何」，但只要在後面加上不同的字，就能問各種「程度、數量、頻率、距離…」，形成一整組實用的疑問副詞片語。這是會考超高頻考點，務必把每一個片語問的重點記清楚。<br><br><b>how 家族一次看懂</b><br>• <b>how many「多少」</b>：問<b>可數</b>名詞的數量。How many books do you have?（你有幾本書？）<br>• <b>how much「多少」</b>：問<b>不可數</b>名詞的量，也問<b>價錢</b>。How much money…？／How much is it?（多少錢？）<br>• <b>how old「幾歲」</b>：問年紀。How old is your dog?（你的狗幾歲？）<br>• <b>how tall「多高」</b>：問身高。How tall are you?（你多高？）<br>• <b>how often「多常」</b>：問頻率，答句常用「次數 + 一段時間」。How often…? → Twice a week.（一週兩次）<br>• <b>how long「多久／多長」</b>：問時間多久或事物的長度。How long does it take?（要花多久？）<br>• <b>how far「多遠」</b>：問距離。How far is it from here?（從這裡有多遠？）<br>• <b>how soon「多快」</b>：問「多久之內」會完成，答句常用「in + 時間」。How soon…? → In ten minutes.（十分鐘後）<br>• <b>how fast「多快」</b>：問<b>速度</b>。How fast can a tiger run?（老虎能跑多快？）<br>• <b>how about = what about「如何」</b>：問意見或提供建議，後面接名詞或 V-ing。How about going swimming?（去游泳如何？）<br>• <b>how come = why「為何」</b>：問原因，但後面句子<b>不可倒裝</b>。<br>• <b>how bad「有多嚴重」</b>：問嚴重程度。How bad is it?（有多嚴重？）<br><br><b>★易錯一：how many vs how much（可數 vs 不可數）</b><br>可數名詞（複數）用 how many：How many apples…？<br>不可數名詞用 how much：How much water…？<br>陷阱：肉類（beef、pork）是不可數，用 how much；但若加上計量詞（pounds of beef 磅），就變可數，改用 how many：How many pounds of beef…？<br><br><b>★易錯二：how soon vs how fast（時間 vs 速度）</b><br>• how soon：問「還要多久才會發生／完成」，答 in + 一段時間（In fifteen minutes.）。<br>• how fast：問「執行動作的速度有多快」，答 80 kilos per hour 之類。<br>例：How soon will you come back?（你多快回來→問時間）vs. How fast can you run?（你能跑多快→問速度）。<br><br><b>★易錯三：how often 的答句格式</b><br>how often 問頻率，答句用「次數 + 一段時間」：once a week、twice a month、three times a year，或 every day。不要用 in ten minutes（那是 how soon 的答法）。<br><br><b>★易錯四：how about / what about 後面接什麼</b><br>後面接名詞或動名詞（V-ing），不接原形動詞：<br>How about this jacket?（名詞）／How about going now?（V-ing）。<br>（誤）How about go now? ✗<br><br><b>★易錯五：how come 不可倒裝</b><br>how come 意同 why，但語序是「how come + 主詞 + 動詞」，不加助動詞、不倒裝：<br>（正）How come you didn't go to school?<br>（誤）How come did you go to school? ✗<br><br><b>比較整理（用答句反推問句）</b><br>答 four people → How many；答 40 dollars → How much；答 nineteen(歲) → How old；答 190 cm → How tall；答 twice a week → How often；答 half an hour → How long；答 two kilos(距離) → How far；答 in ten minutes → How soon；答 80 km/hr → How fast。<br>看到答句就能倒推問句，是會考最愛的出題方式。<br><br><b>記憶口訣</b><br>「many 數個數、much 量與錢、old 年紀 tall 身高、often 頻率 long 時長、far 距離 soon 多久內、fast 比速度」──把答句對號入座，選擇題迎刃而解。",
          "examples": [
            {
              "en": "How many classmates are joining the basketball team this year?",
              "zh": "今年有多少同學要加入籃球隊？"
            },
            {
              "en": "How much does this bubble tea cost with extra pearls?",
              "zh": "這杯珍珠加量的珍奶要多少錢？"
            },
            {
              "en": "How often do you water the plants on your balcony?",
              "zh": "你多常幫陽台上的植物澆水？"
            },
            {
              "en": "How long does it take you to walk from home to school?",
              "zh": "你從家裡走到學校要花多久時間？"
            },
            {
              "en": "How far is the nearest convenience store from here?",
              "zh": "最近的便利商店離這裡有多遠？"
            },
            {
              "en": "How soon can you finish this bowl of noodles?",
              "zh": "你多快能吃完這碗麵？"
            },
            {
              "en": "How about meeting at the library after lunch to study together?",
              "zh": "午餐後在圖書館碰面一起唸書如何？"
            },
            {
              "en": "How come you're wearing your jacket inside out today?",
              "zh": "你今天怎麼把外套穿反了？"
            },
            {
              "en": "How often do you visit your grandparents in the countryside?",
              "zh": "你多久去鄉下探望一次你的祖父母？"
            },
            {
              "en": "How far is it from your house to the train station?",
              "zh": "從你家到火車站有多遠？"
            }
          ]
        },
