            "passage": "My brother Leo is training for his first marathon, so I asked him lots of questions. \"__(1)__ do you run every week to get ready?\" I asked. \"Almost every day,\" he said. \"__(2)__ is the race from the starting line to the finish?\" I wondered. \"About forty-two kilometers,\" he answered. \"Wow, __(3)__ does it take you to finish that?\" \"Around four hours,\" he said, wiping his face. \"__(4)__ pairs of running shoes have you worn out this year?\" I laughed. \"Three so far!\" Then I looked at his water bottle and asked, \"__(5)__ water should you drink during a long run?\" \"A lot,\" he grinned. \"__(6)__ resting for a few minutes before you push yourself again?\" I suggested, and he agreed.",
