            {
              "en": "I finally found the pen that I lost last week.",
              "zh": "我終於找到上禮拜弄丟的那支筆了。"
            },
            {
              "en": "The girl whom you met at the bus stop is my cousin.",
              "zh": "你在公車站遇到的那個女生是我的表妹。"
            },
            {
              "en": "The song which the band played last night is still stuck in my head.",
              "zh": "那個樂團昨晚演奏的歌現在還在我腦中揮之不去。"
