            },
            {
              "en": "The classmate who cheated on the exam was caught by the teacher.",
              "zh": "考試作弊的那位同學被老師抓到了。"
            },
            {
              "en": "Ms. Chen, whom everyone trusts, was chosen as the new principal.",
              "zh": "大家都信任的陳老師被選為新校長。"
            },
            {
              "en": "Take whatever you need from the shelf before you leave.",
              "zh": "離開前，架上的東西你需要什麼就拿吧。"
